msgstr ""
"Lisaks on &kbounce;'il tavapärased &kde; <guimenu>seadistuste</guimenu> ja "
"<guimenu>abi</guimenu>menüü elemendid, mille kohta leiab rohkem teavet &kde; "
"põhialuste käsiraamatu osadest <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-"
"settings\">Menüü Seadistused</ulink> ja <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
"html#menus-help\">Menüü Abi</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Ma soovin muuta mängu välimust. On see võimalik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. To change &kbounce; visual theme you can use "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kbounce;..."
#| "</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kbounce; visual theme you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kbounce;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgstr ""
"Jah. &kbounce;'i teema muutmiseks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guisubmenu>&kbounce;'i "
"seadistamine...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Tegin vea. Kas selle saab tagasi võtta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "&kbounce; ei võimalda <quote>tagasivõtmist</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kbounce; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ei, &kbounce;'i ei saa klaviatuuri abil mängida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kbounce; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kbounce; ei võimalda veel <quote>salvestamist</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Mängu seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kbounce; configuration dialog allows you to select visual themes for "
"&kbounce;."
msgstr ""
"&kbounce;'i seadistustedialoog võimaldab valida &kbounce;'i visuaalse teema."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Uue teema valimiseks vali see lihtsalt loendist. Kõigi nimekirja elementide "
"juures on teena nimest vasakul näha väike eelvaatlus. Valik rakendatakse "
"kohe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select random background pictures from a user defined folder with "
"images."
msgstr ""
"Sa võid valida suvalised taustapildid kasutaja määratud pilte sisaldavast "
"kataloogist."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> button, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled valitud teemaga rahul, klõpsa nupule <guibutton>OK</guibutton>, mis "
"asub dialoogi allosas."

